data.description:
Welcome to 2502 S. Chloe Circle in Fruitport Township.  This 4 bedroom 2 full bath home offers immediate possession. On the main level you will find 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Open concept kitchen with center island, dining room and living room with cathedral ceilings, and sliding door that opens to the deck overlooking the back yard.   In the lower level you will find the 4th bedroom and a large finished family room with gas fireplace. There is pluming in place to add a 3rd bath, along with a roughed in room for possible 5th bedroom if needed.
Now for the good stuff, there is a second two stall garage with heat, for all the toys, storage, maybe a workshop?
Underground sprinkler system and nicely landscaped yard.
All this and conveniently located to shopping and the I96 and US31 Exchange.  Call today for your personal tour.
